{"tid":116244,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"過幾日我生日 男朋友話趁今日星期六黎我屋企開生日party","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T10:18:25.000Z","uid":6527,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e439ccb3588fe56e544c4fdef703824f680eaadb","tid":116244,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"過幾日就到我生日 <br />\n男朋友就話諗住趁今日星期六<br />\n黎我屋企同我屋企人一齊幫我開個生日party<br />\n真係有我心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係其實佢唔知 我既屋企人一早已經去哂旅行<br />\n屋企得番我一個架咋<br />\n呢個係我諗住送比佢既一個驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實本來仲有另一位朋友要黎<br />\n不過佢最近好忙 好似話要去外國拜師<br />\n所以應該都唔會黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就當係為左成全我同我男朋友獨處啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外今日我落足心機 整左好多好野食<br />\n諗住同男朋友二人世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9R6cy65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9R6cy65.jpg&h=9190a4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過整完先發現好似整多左<br />\n唔緊要 我地今晚食唔哂可以留番聽朝食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩男朋友打電話黎話可以要遲一陣先到 <br />\n叫我同大家開住party先<br />\n佢應該估唔到我會比個咁既驚喜佢呢<br />\n真係愈黎愈期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出面好似就黎會落雪 唔知佢係咪塞緊車呢<br />\n我今晚一直都會等佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4546ba818272787c33d22ded502e7ce5e2e3a8c5","tid":116244,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"瘋了"},{"pid":"45aad5eed3164404a975d3c8b130979e0258d7a5","tid":116244,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"無是咁的，零分重作"},{"pid":"6b37cb1f92d1239952d7d588dcac0702e01696e4","tid":116244,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"真人真事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c39a8a8b96e60032fec62b55058cef9f5fe6f85","tid":116244,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee84b3f6d42ef3e7f36b1c7ec55eb718e998456a","tid":116244,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔like雪菜<br />\n但係慘既!"},{"pid":"8b4721e9e1f74a59418096d57c55252512bc1d78","tid":116244,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"買張大D既床3個一齊瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5709c80cc27776cfbc8b3dcff4aa92dd6dd32f2e","tid":116244,"uid":7477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"我愛樓主"},{"pid":"453b947e15098087b9b75171d4f0bd67ba82d558","tid":116244,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我唔like雪菜<br />\n但係慘既!</blockquote><br />\n等待一個人既時候係痛苦既<br />\n但係佢一陣到左我就會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fc5d7e5dff1bfd8acdd694942299d408867408","tid":116244,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"收島風你條仔係條街度同個黑長直攪埋一齊喎"},{"pid":"e1379a52c6c8ba49ec20787a9b0269f7764a32df","tid":116244,"uid":39709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"bitch"},{"pid":"57ee436525ae66f9d24535fb465b5ac4020e8abd","tid":116244,"uid":34363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"6bc667f666f67ce03072467cc52dc22a653f3011","tid":116244,"uid":56599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"毒撚ff真可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ca4f54ae8b4eeed1769cc1593c41f758850bca","tid":116244,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收島風你條仔係條街度同個黑長直攪埋一齊喎</blockquote><br />\n我男朋友好愛我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且一般既黑長直會都唔會睇得上眼架<br />\n畢竟我另外個個朋友都係黑長直 仲要好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢都係揀左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a83235aece8f3641a0c9a1d74457dc6cf50a8f5","tid":116244,"uid":60540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},{"pid":"027c7d61d2d89582d026ac889d9464c819ed8ede","tid":116244,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e43ba5ef405816e8252636c5c7391e05e7b3d41","tid":116244,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂</blockquote><br />\n多謝和紗bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6c7074069152f0807962497b4884218f625cd1","tid":116244,"uid":13212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"動漫台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c46163318bf91c9fde19fdd834152f8541cc79","tid":116244,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動漫台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7432646d28a70